              "free_text": [
                " Double-sided  multistrip silicon detector",
                "DSSSD, 48x48 strips. Detects the nuclei under",
                "investigation, their emitted a particles, and",
                "spontaneous fission fragments.",
                "The focal semiconductor detector is surrounded with an",
                "array of 54 neutron 3He counters in a moderator.",
                "The energy resolution for alpha-particles in the range",
                "of 6 to 10 MeV is ~ 20 keV.",
                "The position resolution of the focal detector is 1mm",
                " (horizontal and vertical).",
                "Four detectors mounted on the sides of the focal",
                "detector. The geometrical detection efficiency is ~70%",
                "of 4PI.",
                "The neutron detector efficiency measured with a 248Cm",
                "source was 45 +- 1%."
              ]
            }
